  27 Feb 2015; Sergey Popov <pinkbyte@gentoo.org> mpi-2.0-r3.ebuild:
  Add ~amd64-fbsd to virtual/mpi as sys-cluster/openmpi is also keyworded

*mpi-2.0-r3 (12 Jul 2013)

  12 Jul 2013; Justin Bronder <jsbronder@gentoo.org> -mpi-2.0-r2.ebuild,
  +mpi-2.0-r3.ebuild:
  add threads as an optional use dep

*mpi-2.0-r2 (09 Jul 2013)

